<%- include('partials/header', { title: 'Password Changed', appName: appName }) %>

<h2>Password Changed Successfully</h2>

<p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>

<p>This email confirms that your password for <%= appName %> has been changed successfully.</p>

<div class="highlight">
    <p><strong>Change Details:</strong></p>
    <p>Date: <%= changeDate %></p>
    <p>Time: <%= changeTime %></p>
    <p>IP Address: <%= ipAddress || 'Not available' %></p>
</div>

<div class="warning">
    <p><strong>Didn't change your password?</strong> If you didn't make this change, your account may be compromised. Please:</p>
    <ul style="margin-left: 20px;">
        <li>Contact our support team immediately</li>
        <li>Try to log in and change your password</li>
        <li>Check for any unauthorized activity</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<p>For your security, we recommend:</p>
<ul style="margin-left: 20px;">
    <li>Using a strong, unique password</li>
    <li>Enabling two-factor authentication</li>
    <li>Keeping your account information up to date</li>
</ul>

<p>If you have any questions or concerns about your account security, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
The <%= appName %> Team</p>

<%- include('partials/footer', { appName: appName }) %>
